for the custom teleports look in the clickingmost and magichandler…

easiest way would be to teleport somewhere, find the coords, and then search the file for the coords

and for the object ids,

not all sources have it…
you may have to find a list either on mopar or in another source,

but if yours does have it, it would be in the notes folder
